cs.NI, cs.GT, cs.SY, cs.CR, cs.IT 

This paper deals with energy balancing in cellular networks, which is a topic related to network infrastructure and communication protocols. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.NI (Networking and Internet Architecture). The paper also discusses the use of relay stations and optimization of energy consumption, which are topics related to game theory (cs.GT) and control systems (cs.SY). Additionally, the paper proposes a predictive model for energy consumption, which is related to cryptography and security (cs.CR) and information theory (cs.IT).
